itemDescription: British Roman Catholic politician and life peer (born 1935)

wikipedia_page.main: Susan Lilian Primrose Cunliffe-Lister, Dowager Countess of Swinton, Baroness Masham of Ilton,  (née Sinclair; born (1935-04-14)14 April 1935) is a crossbench member of the House of Lords. She is the senior life peer.
